❓ Troubleshooting
Error: "next is not a function" -> You installed Mongoose v9. Run npm install mongoose@8 to fix.
Server crashes immediately -> You installed Dotenv v17. Run npm install dotenv@16 to fix.
Database connection fails -> Check your internet connection (MongoDB Atlas requires internet).